          "chat",
          "Chat",
          "CHAT"
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "regex",
        "pattern": "\\b[A-Za-z0-9]{30,50}\\b",
        "message": "Twitch app access token detected in source code. App access tokens provide server-to-server authentication for Twitch applications, enabling access to public Twitch data and API endpoints without user context. Exposing these tokens allows unauthorized API access, potential rate limit abuse, and access to application-level Twitch functionality. Replace with secure credential storage and rotate token immediately.",
