          "Helix",
          "HELIX"
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "regex",
        "pattern": "(?:twitch_|TWITCH_|Twitch|twitch|TWITCH)[_-]?(?:access_token|ACCESS_TOKEN|access-token|accessToken|AccessToken|token|TOKEN|Token|user_token|USER_TOKEN|user-token|userToken|UserToken|oauth_token|OAUTH_TOKEN|oauth-token|oauthToken|OauthToken)[\"'\\s]*[:=][\"'\\s]*[a-z0-9]{30,50}",
        "message": "Twitch access token detected in variable assignment. This token provides authenticated access to Twitch API services including user data, channel management, stream information, and chat functionality. Exposing Twitch tokens enables unauthorized account access, stream manipulation, and potential misuse of user permissions. Store tokens securely using environment variables or secure credential management.",
