        "pattern": "Authorization[\"'\\s]*[:=][\"'\\s]*Bearer\\s+[a-z0-9A-Z]{30,50}",
        "message": "Twitch bearer token detected in Authorization header. Bearer tokens provide direct API authentication for Twitch services and are used in HTTP requests to access protected endpoints. Exposing bearer tokens in authorization headers allows immediate unauthorized access to Twitch API functionality including user data, channel operations, and stream management. Remove hardcoded bearer tokens and use secure credential management.",
